Dialogue: 30,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That way's the long way to...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:30.86,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your memories?!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:32.82,0:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:34.11,0:00:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So this whole time, you can't\Nremember anything that happened...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:38.62,0:00:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:40.24,0:00:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha, why is it that\Nyou think she's Shiina Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:44.75,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already! Because of that Upa!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something she got from her mom.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:50.30,0:00:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kagari's charm...\NOne that she always cherished.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:54.17,0:00:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that, Kana-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:56.34,0:00:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:57.68,0:01:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When they found me collapsed and unconscious,\Nthis is the only thing I had with me.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:03.73,0:01:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Unconscious?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:05.27,0:01:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lying near the border of Chiba Prefecture
Dialogue: 30,0:01:08.11,0:01:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,when a priest passing by\Nmust have stumbled across me.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:11.36,0:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did you end up at Lukako's?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:13.94,0:01:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They felt it wasn't right for a girl\Nto stay long at a practicing temple.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:19.16,0:01:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At Big Bro Luka's? To think she was so close!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:23.25,0:01:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, am I... Is my name actually Shiina Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:27.79,0:01:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the two of you know something about me?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I—
Dialogue: 30,0:01:32.00,0:01:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Calm down...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:35.59,0:01:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kana-san, does hearing the name\NShiina Kagari make you remember anything?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:41.81,0:01:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:44.52,0:01:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But... In a way, it sounds very nostalgic.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:49.23,0:01:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, that person just now...
Dialogue: 30,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Mayuri?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:54.90,0:02:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri-san... was her name?
Dialogue: 30,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari...
Dialogue: 30,0:02:01.91,0:02:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina Kagari...
Dialogue: 30,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina Kagari.
Dialogue: 30,0:02:08.37,0:02:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2036... she was Mayuri's... daughter.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying Kana-sa—I mean...
Dialogue: 30,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-san is somebody\Nthat you know, Suzuha-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I suppose you could say that.
Dialogue: 30,0:03:54.15,0:03:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, don't you know where\NKagari-san lived, or somebody in her family?
Dialogue: 30,0:03:59.40,0:04:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, actually...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:02.15,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She moved away when they were just kids.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:06.16,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha doesn't know anything after that.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:10.20,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but at least we found out your real name.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:15.67,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari-san's name is Shiina Kagari, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:18.75,0:04:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're just like me!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:23.18,0:04:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Mayushii is Shiina Mayuri.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:25.97,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina Mayuri-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:29.39,0:04:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard from Luka-kun,\Nbut is it true you have amnesia?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:34.64,0:04:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:35.52,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So... You don't even remember\Nanything about who you are?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:42.32,0:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:44.11,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This... has to be so painful for you.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:47.49,0:04:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, that means you forgot\Nabout all the people you love, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:52.00,0:04:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... the saddest thing\Nthat can happen to someone, I think.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:57.25,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um, I... I don't know how to put it, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:02.09,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii wants to help you out too!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:04.22,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's do our best!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:13.77,0:05:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:15.39,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason I'm really happy...\Nto hear that from you.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just Mayushii.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:25.07,0:05:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I-If there's anything\NI can do to help, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:37.08,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we found Shiina Kagari ourselves.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where at?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:41.75,0:05:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying at a shrine of a friend of mine.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:45.13,0:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was found collapsed at the edge of Chiba.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's lost all of her memories.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:53.06,0:05:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:53.93,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Any update on the crew\Nthat was searching for her?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:57.27,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing yet.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:59.65,0:06:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. This time of year\Nis busy enough as it is.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Work is work.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Should I keep at it?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, it'd help a lot if you did.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They found her...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:33.43,0:06:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:36.02,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the big idea, Professor?!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:39.39,0:06:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, it's a message from him?!
Dialogue: 30,0:06:41.90,0:06:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even close.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you and Leskinen just drop it already?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, love as a concept\Nis completely worthless.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's where you're wrong.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:56.29,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, your love life\Nis my most curious field of study.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:01.63,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, there's no point in treating\Nme like one of your test subjects.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:05.80,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never allow myself to be\Nfooled by the delusion of love.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:10.26,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A shame.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Professor...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:20.39,0:07:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry for everything...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:25.36,0:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii wants to help out too,\Nso say if you need something!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:29.07,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Lukako, got a minute?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:37.04,0:07:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to keep Kagari-san from going outside?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that's...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:41.41,0:07:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If she has to, make\Nsure someone goes with her.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As for why... I can't say yet.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what you say, Okabe-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:51.30,0:07:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:53.80,0:07:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know\Nwho else was searching for Kagari.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:57.18,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And until we do, it's best if\Nwe take all the precautions we can.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's great that\Nwe finally found Kagari-tan.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:07.98,0:08:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can relax for once.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:10.15,0:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:14.03,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly the relieved face I was expecting...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:17.33,0:08:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... Where has she been until now?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Amnesia, huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:24.21,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering the same thing myself.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:27.00,0:08:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like you can do\Nanything about it in the first place.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:30.84,0:08:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that, don't they say\Nit comes back out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do now is wait.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:36.72,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be true, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:39.39,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,\Nwe could try scaring it out of her...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:43.10,0:08:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He— u-uh—
Dialogue: 30,0:08:50.78,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh— h-he u-uh u-uh...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:58.12,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do something like that.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:02.12,0:09:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear... a voice...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagari!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Okarin...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:27.73,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we supposed to be going\Nto the shrine for New Year’s?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:33.53,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then why... are we in this weird situation?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:37.41,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you've got something to say,\Nthen speak up nice and loud.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We were hoping to enter the lab, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:50.38,0:09:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Why not?! This is tyranny!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:53.46,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised to meet the others here\Nto go to the shrine together for New Year’s…
Dialogue: 30,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:08.14,0:10:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nae!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so adorable!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you are, you're my daughter!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're hurting me, Dad.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing she looks nothing like—
Dialogue: 30,0:10:19.61,0:10:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I can't wait! I'm so excited\Nto see Big Sis Mayuri as a shrine priestess!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:26.54,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You listen to the girls and behave, all right?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:29.12,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not coming along?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Got some business to take care of.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:34.75,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for that, I wouldn't be leaving\Nmy cutie daughter in your care, would I?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:40.09,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And let me be clear,\Nif anything happens to Nae...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:44.35,0:10:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:45.89,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later, Dad!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:49.23,0:10:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's get moving!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:51.19,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, before that...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:54.11,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're forgetting something important.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:58.74,0:11:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,New Year!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't wait to see Mayushii's\Nshrine priestess cosplay!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:04.53,0:11:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly! It's not cosplay today,\Nit's her uniform!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:09.71,0:11:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Suzuha-san working there too?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be fun.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:13.96,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a shrine priestess sister is one thing...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:16.21,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you've gone that far, might as\Nwell make her a nurse while you're at it
Dialogue: 30,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and push her {\i1}moe{\i} score through the roof.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The perverseness is strong with Hashida-san.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:24.93,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:27.72,0:11:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it was Mayuri's idea, but she\Ngot recruited to work as a shrine priestess.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:35.11,0:11:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to you anyways.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:38.82,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, aren't you attending\Nan American university, Hiyajo-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your research sounds really cool!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:46.95,0:11:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it again? Aye-ayes?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The lemur?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's AI, Fubuki-chan.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:52.17,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! That!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:54.00,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,AI, as in you research\Nartificial intelligence, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:58.34,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really interested in that, actually!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:06.93,0:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay over there?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:10.02,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing... Let's go.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin! Over here, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:19.61,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:22.57,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New nyaa!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:27.95,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! It's a shrine priestess paradise!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this heaven?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha-san, you're lovely!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:38.00,0:12:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:40.09,0:12:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great on you, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:46.93,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Try saying... Bend over,\NBig Brother, it's time for your shot.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:54.44,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit saying crap like that!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you're not progressing with Mom!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You two sure get along well.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well yeah, because she's my daugh—
Dialogue: 30,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Would you like to offer saké?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:16.87,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or how about a fortune slip?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... believe you.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:23.01,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, did I do something?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka-kun is as beautiful as ever.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not—
Dialogue: 30,0:13:30.60,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to believe it.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that a boy?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:34.10,0:13:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to see proof?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha?! How so?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:44.07,0:13:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Is it good?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you look great in it.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:56.87,0:14:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri-san didn't want to believe us\Nwhen we told her that a hundred times.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept worrying if you'd like it.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You weren't supposed to say that.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:08.13,0:14:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh! But you were worried\Nabout the same thing too.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Yeah, because for someone like me...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:15.56,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! You look gorgeous!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Okarin?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:22.11,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty good.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:31.95,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky you, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, I like it!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shocked.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's exactly like Kurisu.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:45.21,0:14:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:46.26,0:14:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they look almost identical.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:49.38,0:14:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't say I agree.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:57.43,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,About Amadeus, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:59.52,0:15:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Things can't stay as they are,\Nor you'll never have closure.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:03.36,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to make a decision\Nbefore the year gets too far.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:18.58,0:15:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 30,0:15:20.46,0:15:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess they didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lintahlo!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor?!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, Lintahlo!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:33.64,0:15:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them to come since\Nit's a special occasion.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are shrine maidens?!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, famous shamans, where?!{Where are the Japanese shaman girls, Lintalho ?}
Dialogue: 30,0:15:41.19,0:15:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamans?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean the shrine priestesses.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:45.27,0:15:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all done for today.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:47.19,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all about to leave\Nsince they're done cleaning.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:51.15,0:15:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Cow! That's why I said\Nwe should have come earlier!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that couldn't stop shopping.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:57.91,0:16:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Let's go visit the shrine.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:00.75,0:16:04.63,On Top,,0,0,0,,No! You've got to wash your hands here first!\NAnd don't walk in the middle of the path!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:02.78,0:16:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:04.63,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Luka-kun's mom gave us\Na ton of New Year's food!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:08.80,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:11.05,0:16:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rintaro! We'll see you later!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? You're leaving already?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He says there's no point\Nin staying without shrine priestesses.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:19.47,0:16:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch you later! Bye!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:21.93,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Took longer than expected.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure did.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, we should get going ourselves.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:32.99,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. I'll have to call it a day.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not coming to the lab?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:39.95,0:16:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a shortage of staff at work. Sorry...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:43.92,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... That's too bad.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to come back\Nand play another day!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:52.13,0:16:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we head back?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone ready for a New Year's party?!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:59.97,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it one more time!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year, everyone!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:04.81,0:17:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:07.77,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mmm! This {\i1}zoni{\i} soup hits the spot!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:12.99,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from MayQueen's New Year's menu, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I'm tasting a bit of Faris-tan?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:18.82,0:17:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hashida-san, you're such a pervert.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,These beans are delicious.\NThey seem packed with nutrition.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Help yourself, Nae-chan!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:27.63,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,These {\i1}kinton{\i} are yummy too!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:30.13,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no way I could eat all that...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It you don't eat up, you'll never get big!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Down the hatch!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:40.93,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Are we already out of tea, nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:43.93,0:17:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we'll run to the store and buy some.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hello!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the landlord guy!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:54.28,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Done with your shrine visit?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the others at?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We're throwing a little party.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Us two are just hitting the store.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:01.78,0:18:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? In that case,\NI'll stop by and pick up Nae later.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:05.29,0:18:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell Okabe to let me\Nknow when your party is over?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:20.01,0:18:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:22.56,0:18:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:26.48,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, nya! I like, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:30.23,0:18:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Senpai? Where in the world are...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that where I think it is?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:36.90,0:18:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:40.91,0:18:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend of Maho-nyan's, nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:43.45,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, um... I'm...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:47.62,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A person from overseas, nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:49.58,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a person, I'm artificial intelligence.\NThat is, an AI created by Maho-senpai.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,AI?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a lemur!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Is that really AI?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:06.22,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You must all be members of Okabe-san's lab.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:11.94,0:19:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Amadeus, an artificial intelligence\Nbased off the memories of Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:19.61,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:23.20,0:19:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I take it all of you were\Nacquaintances of the original me?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:26.87,0:19:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, actually it's more like...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:29.50,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about you from your article in {\i1}Science Magazine{\i}.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:32.71,0:19:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Though, if you read that magazine,\Nyou must be interested in science.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:38.01,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well... I sort of specialize\Nin networks and systems.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:43.68,0:19:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Miss AI? Are you part of\Na game or something? Love & Death?
Dialogue: 30,0:19:48.68,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a game.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:50.23,0:19:56.90,On Top,,0,0,0,,I'm right here, listening to the\Nconversation and talking back to you.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:53.31,0:19:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After saying all those things to you,
Dialogue: 30,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,bringing her out here...
Dialogue: 30,0:19:56.90,0:19:59.86,On Top,,0,0,0,,I think of what I want\Nto say and talk to you.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:57.48,0:19:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:07.28,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it might be better this way.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:11.79,0:20:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, but I have to keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:16.54,0:20:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Kagari resembles Kurisu in\Na way, she's not Kurisu herself.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:22.09,0:20:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Amadeus too. Even if it's based off\Nof her, it exists as a separate entity.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:28.72,0:20:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let her drag me down...\Nis what you wanted to say to me, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:39.48,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She protected it all...\Nthis world with Mayuri and everyone.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:44.11,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have to keep protecting it...\Nwithout ever looking back.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:48.16,0:20:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuha... She may not be\Nconvinced at this point, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:52.08,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we know\Nabsolutely nothing about Kagari.
Dialogue: 30,0:20:55.42,0:20:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But, someday...
Dialogue: 30,0:20:58.21,0:21:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, isn't Okabe-san—
Dialogue: 30,0:21:02.26,0:21:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:04.84,0:21:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It cut off all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? My phone seems\Nto be working just fine...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:13.98,0:21:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's up?\NI can't connect to the Amadeus server...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:21.78,0:21:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My watch isn't working...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:25.40,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange...\NI just wound it not long ago...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Think the server is updating or something?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:34.83,0:21:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is, I never heard about it.
Dialogue: 30,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okabe Rintaro!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:48.64,0:21:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A surprise?
Dialogue: 30,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:53.68,0:21:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 30,0:21:56.89,0:21:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 30,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 30,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...is this?!
